span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I got to this state, but not sure how to iterate through the Finset explicitly</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Œπ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Finset</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Œπ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Finset</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">univ</span>\n<span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Œπ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"